# <type>: <subject>
# │       │
# │       └─⫸ Summary in present tense. Not capitalized. No period at the end.
# │
# └─⫸ Type: feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|test|chore

# Examples:
# feat: add guitar isolation using Demucs AI
# fix: prevent NaN values in tone matcher
# docs: update README with installation steps
# test: add frequency analyzer unit tests
# refactor: simplify profile generation logic

# Body (optional):
# More detailed explanation. Wrap at 72 chars.
#
# - Why this change was made
# - Any relevant context
# - Links to issues/tickets

# Footer (optional):
# Breaking Changes: describe what broke and migration path
# Closes: #123
# See also: #456, #789





